# ğŸ“Œ **Quick Summary Table**

| Name           | Type | Weight      | Best For               |
| -------------- | ---- | ----------- | ---------------------- |
| KDE Plasma     | DE   | Medium      | Desktop, gaming        |
| GNOME          | DE   | Heavy       | Modern workflow        |
| XFCE           | DE   | Light       | Old laptops, stability |
| LXQt           | DE   | Very light  | Low-end PCs            |
| Cinnamon       | DE   | Medium      | Beginners              |
| Deepin         | DE   | Heavy       | Aesthetic users        |
| i3 / Sway      | WM   | Ultra-light | Power users            |
| Hyprland       | WM   | Light       | Tiling + animations    |
| Xmonad / bspwm | WM   | Ultra-light | Advanced users         |

